      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to an exacting standard, preserving its showroom-floor integrity in every discernible detail. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, original cabin environment, this unit represents the zenith of its class. We invite discerning enthusiasts to inspect a vehicle that remains indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade example for those who demand absolute excellence.",
