    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits a concours-level aesthetic, featuring flawless exterior surfacing and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Mechanically, the vehicle has been subjected to rigorous verification to ensure peak performance. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents an unparalleled acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
