    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering razor-sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure total structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the car retains its original VIN tags on all panels and sits on pristine Style 67 forged wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance.",
